#define MESSAGE_HELP "\
All statistics, information and error messages can be seen in main area of Telmon window.\n\
Content of main area is automatically updated, or it can be updated manually by pressing\n\
'Update' button located in menu area at lower part of Telmon window.\n\n\
Server to be monitored can be selected from the drop down menu located above the button area.\n\
Only one server can be monitored at a time by one Telmon instance.\n\n\
BUTTONS AND MENUES ON THE BOTTOM\n\n\
Monitor:\n\
  Select which server program to monitor.\n\n\
Info:\n\
  Display version and license information.\n\n\
Help:\n\
  Display this help message.\n\n\
Update:\n\
  Update all text fields immediately.\n\n\
History (opens in new window):\n\
  Display history chart for selected server program.\n\n\
Settings (opens in new window):\n\
  Select if settings are saved when program terminates normally.\n\n\
Quit:\n\
  Close all open resources and terminate program immediately.\
"
